<p>And that&rsquo;s it.  If you want to try this out, my public key is listed with the centralized GPG public key authority.  My address is: <a href="&#x6d;&#x61;&#105;&#108;&#x74;&#x6f;&#x3a;&#99;&#104;&#114;&#105;&#x73;&#64;&#99;&#115;&#x66;&#x69;&#x65;&#x6c;&#100;&#115;&#x2e;&#99;&#x6f;&#x6d;">&#x63;&#x68;&#x72;&#105;&#115;&#x40;&#99;&#x73;&#102;&#105;&#101;&#x6c;&#100;&#115;&#x2e;&#99;&#x6f;&#109;</a></p>

<p>If you want to learn more about encryption, I would <em>strongly</em> suggest beginning with <a href="https://www.schneier.com/">Bruce Schenier&rsquo;s</a> blog.</p>
